high_descs: Turn to your left and go along the counter on your right until you reach the wall, then turn left to face the round white table.
Pick up the potato that is on the table behind the knives.
Turn left and go along the counter on your left until you come to the stove.
Cook the potato in the microwave above the stove.
Turn around and retrace your path along the counter to the the round white table.
Put the potato on the table, just off the handle end of the nearest knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato onto a round kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk all the way to the table in the far corner of the room.
Pick up the potato off the table.
Turn around and walk around the counter tops all the way to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Turn around and walk around the counters back to the white table.
Place the potato on the table to the right of the toilet paper roll.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and go between the kitchen counter and the white table, then turn left and face the table.
Pick up the potato from in between the knife and the mug.
Go over to face the stove with the potato.
Put the potato in the microwave above the stove, cook it, and then take it out again.
Go back to the same spot facing the table.
Put the potato down on the table between the knife closest to the edge and the roll of paper towels.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato on the table.
